Lance is a recurring character in {{aniseries|PTS}}. He debuted in ''[[EP235|Talkin' 'Bout an Evolution]]'' where he assisted in calming the [[Lance's Gyarados|Red Gyarados]] of the [[Lake of Rage]]. He later returned in {{aniseries|RS}} during the climax of the [[Team Aqua]] and [[Team Magma]] arc, and took part in the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] in {{aniseries|JN}}.
